          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 400,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9833,
            "LocalizeKR": "오래 방치한 원두라 그런지 맛이 별로네.",
            "LocalizeJP": "古い豆ってどうしてこう\n美味しくないんだろ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 410,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6830,
            "LocalizeKR": "로망이라…… 그렇네.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ロマン……かぁ。\n……そうだね。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 420,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10340,
            "LocalizeKR": "그 로망이 없었더라면, 여기까지 오지 못했을 테니까.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ロマンがなかったら、\nここまで来られなかった\nだろうし。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 430,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5970,
            "LocalizeKR": "어릴 때, 비밀 기지가 갖고 싶었던 적은 없었어?",
            "LocalizeJP": "小さい頃にさ、\n秘密基地に憧れたりしなかった？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 440,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6000,
            "LocalizeKR": "하지만 막상 실제로 만들어 보니 생각과 많이 다르더라고.",
            "LocalizeJP": "でも、実際に作ってみると\n思ってたのと全然違って……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 450,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10200,
            "LocalizeKR": "좁고, 불편하고, 할 수 있는 것도 그다지 없고……",
            "LocalizeJP": "狭いし、あんまり\nできることもなくてさ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 460,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8700,
            "LocalizeKR": "꿈꿔왔던 현실은 언제나 그런 모습이었던 것 같아.",
            "LocalizeJP": "なんか……\n夢と現実を突きつけられた\nみたいだったんだよね。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 470,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10470,
            "LocalizeKR": "이상적인 어른의 모습도, SRT의 생활도.",
            "LocalizeJP": "理想の大人も、SRTの生活も。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 480,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4500,
            "LocalizeKR": "하지만 그 로망 덕분이었을까.",
            "LocalizeJP": "でも、\nだからこそっていうのかな。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 490,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13000,
            "LocalizeKR": "현실의 불편함도 이제는 기묘한 풍미로 느껴져.",
            "LocalizeJP": "現実がどんな形でも、\n味があるって思うように\nなったっていうか。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1602001,
            "DisplayOrder": 500,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 6,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9000,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님. 로망을 잔뜩 탄 싸구려 커피의 맛은 어때?",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生はさ、ロマンが詰まった\n古いコーヒー、どう思う？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle6",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_06_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16020,
